sentences: Ragnar "Raggi" Þórhallsson (born 6 March 1987) is an Icelandic musician.
The band then entered the 2010 annual Icelandic music competition Músíktilraunir, which they won.
They soon released their debut studio album My Head Is an Animal in late 2011.
After a successful first album, the band released their second studio album Beneath the Skin in 2015.
